  2. Added new modules tensorflow/python/layers and tensorflow/contrib/linalg to tf_python.cmake

@aselle, I made a TODO item for you in cwise_ops_test.py to restore those data types once the question around the "+ 0.1" is resolved.

I'm merging this PR now.
